OL,3,CBrazen CCTV and 10,00 phones seized:
OL,4,CInside the Met's phone theft crackdown
OL,6,FCCTV of brazen mobile phone snatch and
OL,7,Fgrabs were released by the Met Police
OL,9,FShocking footage of brazen phone
OL,10,Fthefts in London have been released by
OL,11,Fthe Metropolitan Police, as the force
OL,12,Fseized 1,000 stolen mobiles during a
OL,13,Fweek long crackdown.
OL,15,FOfficers arrested 230 people across
OL,16,Fthe capital, as part of a special
OL,17,Foperation to stop the #50million a-
OL,18,Fyear trade in stolen phones.
