OL,3,CBrazen CCTV and 10,00 phones seized:
OL,4,CInside the Met's phone theft crackdown
OL,6,FThe Met is boosting efforts to tackle
OL,7,Fthe crimes, including increasing
OL,8,Fpatrols and plain-clothed operations
OL,9,Fin hotspot areas, including the West
OL,10,FEnd and Westminster, where nearly 40
OL,11,Fper cent of phone thefts occur.
OL,13,FIncreased patrols in Westminster saw
OL,14,F17 arrests for robbery and theft.
OL,16,FIn Hackney and Haringey, officers made
OL,17,F15 arrests linked to the operation,
OL,18,Fincluding a 15-year-old boy on an
OL,19,Fillegal electric bike who was found
OL,20,Fwith #1,000 in cash and a large knife.
