OL,3,CBrazen CCTV and 10,00 phones seized:
OL,4,CInside the Met's phone theft crackdown
OL,6,FAt the same time, officers are using
OL,7,Fphone-tracking data and intelligence
OL,8,Fto pursue those handling stolen
OL,9,Fdevices.
OL,11,FLater today (Thursday), the Home
OL,12,FSecretary will chair a summit with law
OL,13,Fenforcement bodies and industry
OL,14,Ffocused on tackling smartphone thefts.
OL,16,FOne of the items that will be raised
OL,17,Fby the Met's Deputy Commissioner, Dame
OL,18,FLynne Owens, will be strengthening
OL,19,Fsecurity on phones so stolen devices
OL,20,Fcannot be easily resold.
