OL,3,CBrazen CCTV and 10,00 phones seized:
OL,4,CInside the Met's phone theft crackdown
OL,6,FCommander Owain Richards, who is
OL,7,Fleading the Met's response to phone
OL,8,Fthefts, said: "We are seeing phone
OL,9,Fthefts on an industrial scale, fuelled
OL,10,Fby criminals making millions by being
OL,11,Fable to easily sell on stolen devices
OL,12,Feither here or abroad."
OL,14,FPhone-tracking data and intelligence
OL,15,Fis being used to trace people using
OL,16,Fstolen devices.
