OL,3,CBrazen CCTV and 10,00 phones seized:
OL,4,CInside the Met's phone theft crackdown
OL,6,FGang arrested after owners were robbed
OL,7,Fof their phones in the capital and the
OL,8,Fgang used them to steal thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds from bank accounts, as Sam
OL,10,FLeader reports
OL,12,FLast year four members of a gang were
OL,13,Fsentenced to "a combined 18 years"
OL,14,Fafter handling more than 5,000 stolen
OL,15,Fphones, the force said.
OL,17,FThey were tracked down after multiple
OL,18,Fvictims reported phone theft in the
OL,19,Fsame location, it added.
