OL,3,CBrazen CCTV and 10,00 phones seized:
OL,4,CInside the Met's phone theft crackdown
OL,6,FMr Richards said "we need help from
OL,7,Fpartners and industry to do more" and
OL,8,Fthe force is "calling on tech
OL,9,Fcompanies to make stolen phones
OL,10,Funusable".
OL,12,FKaya Comer-Schwartz, London's deputy
OL,13,Fmayor for policing and crime, said
OL,14,F"personal robbery" has fallen by 13%
OL,15,Fin the capital compared to the same
OL,16,Fperiod last year.
