OL,3,CBrazen CCTV and 10,00 phones seized:
OL,4,CInside the Met's phone theft crackdown
OL,6,FShe added: "But there is more to do.
OL,7,FAs the criminal demand for high-value
OL,8,Fmobile phones continues to grow
OL,9,Fglobally, the Mayor and I are clear
OL,10,Fthat companies must go further and
OL,11,Ffaster to make it harder for stolen
OL,12,Fphones to be sold on, repurposed and
OL,13,Freused illegally.
OL,15,F"We'll continue to work with leading
OL,16,Fmobile phone companies, the Home
OL,17,FSecretary and Met leaders to find
OL,18,Finnovative solutions to end the
OL,19,Fscourge of mobile phone crime."
